    <releaseNotes># Version 3.0.6

================

## Changes

* Compatible with new MacOS Catalina requirements.
* Minor changes to logging detail levels.

## Bugfixes

* Fix sharing indicator sizing issue in some mixed screen DPI scenarios.

================

# Version 3.0.5

================

## Changes

* Reduce amount of logging, especially metrics.

## Bugfixes

* Remove several potential crash scenarios.
* Minor bugfixes.

================

# Version 3.0.4

================

## Bugfixes

* Fix cursor scaling and positioning on MacOS.
* Minor bugfixes.

================

# Version 3.0.3

================
      
## Changes

* Make code aware of microphone privacy settings in MacOS.

## Bugfixes

* Fix errors where network issues could result in corrupt downloads.
* Improve validation of downloaded upgrades on MacOS to ensure upgrades are not left half-finished.

================

# Version 3.0.2

================

## Changes

* Added confirmation dialog for ending calls.
* Minor improvements to UI in some error situations.

## Bugfixes

* Stop showing call controls in all cases where call controls are unavailable.
* Handle disabled and unsupported systems correctly.
